machine_start_gcode:
PRINT_START BED=[first_layer_bed_temperature] HOTEND=[first_layer_temperature] CHAMBER=[chamber_temperature]
G92 E0.0 ; reset extruder
G1 X{first_layer_print_min[0]} Y{first_layer_print_min[1]-5} Z0.8 F6000.0 ; position 5mm down from the lower left of the first layer
G1 X{first_layer_print_min[0]+30} Y{first_layer_print_min[1]-5} E15 F180.0 ; extrude 15mm of filament in the x direction
G92 E0.0 ; reset extruder
G1 E-0.5 F2100 ; small retraction
G1 X{first_layer_print_min[0]+40} F6000.0 ; move an additional 10mm without extruding
G92 E0.0 ; reset extruder
